01:18:19.000 --> 01:18:21.082
That's terrific. That's great.

01:18:21.560 --> 01:18:23.847
That's beautiful.

01:18:24.200 --> 01:18:25.531
Frank.

01:18:28.200 --> 01:18:31.329
