01:22:20.720 --> 01:22:22.529
Pygmies!

01:22:30.080 --> 01:22:31.127
Roy?

01:22:31.280 --> 01:22:34.170
- <i>Medical</i> Group.
- Yes, Dr. Klein, please.

01:22:34.320 --> 01:22:39.008
