01:24:53.480 --> 01:24:54.811
Did you call security?

01:25:09.560 --> 01:25:11.324
Did you give me this?

01:25:11.480 --> 01:25:13.482
- Yes.
- Why?

01:25:13.640 --> 01:25:18.043
- Because you don't need medication.
